## Alternative: Git Template

If not using npm, create GitHub template repo:

```bash
# User runs
npx degit megacampus/claude-agents my-project/.claude
```

Simpler but no version management.

## Recommendation

Start with **npm package** for professional distribution:
1. Better versioning (semver)
2. Easy updates (`npx create-claude-agents@latest`)
3. Standard ecosystem integration
4. Can add to existing projects

